 - Send Agents by dragging and dropping them on planets
 - By spending time on planets, you earn Resources and Influence after each round
 - Each planet has it's own Councilor with varying Demands from other planets
 - Your agents can gain a Councilor card signifying your endorsement from a Councilor by
 building enough Influence on them and fulfilling their Demands
 - The Councilor card carried by an Agent must be transferred to the Player in order to gain winning points
 - Withdraw an Agent back to base to get their Councilor card
 - Moving, sending and withdrawing an Agent costs one (1) Favor-card from the Player's hand
 - Each round ends with an Event phase where Agents are rewarded Resources or Favor cards (transferred to Player)
 - Before each Event phase, all remaining hand cards are discarded
